# Renderer UI Rules

## Data fetching — React Query only
Never use `useState + useEffect` for IPC data. Always use service hooks:
```ts
import { useDocuments, usePostings, useJobQueue } from '@/services';
const { data, isLoading } = useDocuments();
```

## i18n
```ts
// ✅ correct
import { useTranslation } from '@/lib/i18n';
// ❌ never
import { useTranslation } from 'react-i18next';
```

## Motion tokens
```ts
// ✅ correct
import { transition, variants, stagger } from '@/lib/motion';
<motion.div transition={transition.normal}>
// ❌ never
<motion.div transition={{ duration: 0.18, ease: [0.22, 1, 0.36, 1] }}>
```

## Brand colors
```tsx
// ✅ correct
className="text-brand-soft bg-brand/15 border-brand/30"
// ❌ never
className="text-[#c084fc] bg-[#a855f7]/15"
```

## UI primitives to use
| Need | Import |
|------|--------|
| Button | `@/components/ui/Button` |
| Input | `@/components/ui/Input` |
| TextArea | `@/components/ui/TextArea` |
| Dropdown | `@/components/ui/SelectDropdown` |
| Modal | `@/components/ui/ModalShell` |
| Empty state | `@/components/ui/EmptyState` |
| Skeleton | `@/components/ui/LoadingSkeleton` |
| Card | `@/components/ui/GlassCard` |
| Page wrapper | `@/components/layout/PageShell` |
| AI stream text | `@/components/ui/StreamingText` |
| Selectable tile | `@/components/ui/OptionTile` |

## File placement
- `features/X/components/` — components owned by only route X
- `components/ui/` — shared across multiple features
- `services/` — all IPC/React Query hooks
- `lib/machines/` — state machines for complex flows (3+ states)

## State machines
Use `useMachine` for any wizard or multi-step flow:
```ts
import { useMachine } from '@/hooks/use-machine';
import { autopilotWizardMachine } from '@/lib/machines/autopilot-wizard.machine';
const [state, send, { busy }] = useMachine(autopilotWizardMachine, 'step_0');
```
